&lt;p&gt;This role is not delivery‑led. Success here means being the first consultant through the door, helping clients understand &lt;em&gt;why&lt;/em&gt; AI matters, &lt;em&gt;where&lt;/em&gt; it creates value, and &lt;em&gt;what&lt;/em&gt; problems are worth solving, before solutions are designed or delivered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will act as the &lt;strong&gt;strategic bridge between our customers and our AI engineering teams&lt;/strong&gt;, owning the commercial and advisory narrative from early discussions through to winning client approval.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are particularly interested in candidates from strategic consultancies and top‑tier consulting firms and leading strategy houses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead &lt;strong&gt;front‑end, client‑facing engagements,&lt;/strong&gt; owning early‑stage conversations with senior business and executive stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a &lt;strong&gt;trusted advisor&lt;/strong&gt; to C‑suite and senior leaders, helping articulate business challenges and opportunities where AI can create measurable value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape and &lt;strong&gt;lead pre‑sales conversations&lt;/strong&gt;, including discovery workshops, executive briefings, and value‑focused discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define &lt;strong&gt;AI‑enabled business use cases, problem statements, and transformation roadmaps&lt;/strong&gt; aligned to strategic and commercial outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business priorities into clear, well‑structured briefs for AI and engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and &lt;strong&gt;shape winning proposals, from opportunity framing and value narrative through to executive‑level pitches and client sign‑off.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop business cases, ROI narratives, and investment justifications to support client decision‑making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with technical teams to ensure alignment between business intent and technical execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay informed on AI, GenAI, and digital transformation trends, with a focus on business impact rather than technical depth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in management consulting, strategy consulting, or senior business advisory roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in strategic consultancy strongly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience leading pre‑sales, advisory, or early‑stage transformation conversations with enterprise clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to &lt;strong&gt;lead, shape, and win client proposals, from initial opportunity framing through to executive‑level pitch and client sign‑off.&lt;/strong&

