&lt;p class=&quot;p-large&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A Full Stack Professional is trained to understand what is going on between these two interfaces and possesses the variety of software skills needed to work on both. People with a strong desire to learn a multitude of technologies and programming languages with a can-do attitude will thrive in this role. Full Stack Professionals are problem-solvers, working in a fast-paced, collaborative office environment alongside other engineers.&lt;/p&gt;
