&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;AI &amp;amp; Applications Solution Architect &lt;/strong&gt;with a strong technical foundation and sharp business acumen. You will help organisations elevate their software strategies by embedding AI capabilities and modern app architectures into their products and platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
