&lt;li&gt;You will maintain effective internal relationships with sales, technical, product and delivery colleagues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be confident in providing technical support during sales pitches and proposals and will help to identify and promote additional value add services.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
